               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-1843" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1843" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1843" type="surname" value="BENNETT"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1843" type="given" value="CLARA"></interp>CLARA BENNETT</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the daughter of Thomas Bennett, a beer-seller—the prisoner came to my father's on the 10th of August for half a pint of porter—she put down a shilling—I put it into my mouth, and nearly bit it in half—I said it was a bad one—she said, "Oh is it?"—she paid me with a good shilling, and took up the bad one, and went away.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. PAYNE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Did you know her before? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No, she was there a little while—I was at Union-hall on another charge, and saw her there, and recognized her—I know it was her, because I went after her, she came back and abused me—she went next door, and bought a sheet of paper.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-1844" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1844" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1844" type="surname" value="BROSTER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1844" type="given" value="EMMA"></interp>EMMA BROSTER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am bar-maid at the New-inn, Westminster-bridge-road. On the 11th of August the prisoner came for half a pint of porter—she gave me a bad shilling—I told her it was bad, and she gave me a half-crown—I gave her the change—I then called Mr. Williams, my employer, and marked the shilling in his presence—he gave it to the officer immediately.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> Had you ever seen the prisoner before? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes—she had uttered a bad shilling a week previous.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-1845" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1845" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1845" type="surname" value="BOWDLEY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1845" type="given" value="JANE ANN"></interp>JANE ANN BOWDLEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am bar-maid at the Old Red Lion, Westminster-bridge—the prisoner came there on the 11th of August for half a pint of porter, which came to 1<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—she gave me a shilling to take for it—I saw di<lb></lb>rectly it was a bad one—I took it to my master, and gave it to him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> Had you ever seen her before? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No, I dare say she was there five minutes—I took particular notice of her, because the po<lb></lb>liceman had been in.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-1846" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1846" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1846" type="surname" value="MACKINTOSH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1846" type="given" value="ALPHONSO"></interp>ALPHONSO MACKINTOSH</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the master of Bowdley. On the 11th of August the prisoner was at my bar—Bowdley gave me a bad shilling—I marked it, called the policeman, and gave it him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-1847" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1847" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
